  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2731590/extras/8864ebf8bcfbe519409c58ec1d0f7862.poster.avif?t=1768428581\" width=614 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2731590/extras/8864ebf8bcfbe519409c58ec1d0f7862.webm?t=1768428581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2731590/extras/8864ebf8bcfbe519409c58ec1d0f7862.mp4?t=1768428581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Block Shop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are one of the final candidates in our search for the new Block Shop Operator. Do you have the problem-solving skills, resourcefulness, and intellect to fill this important role? Only one way to find out... </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Block Shop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Block shop is an automation puzzle game in which basic blocks are transformed and combined to create increasingly complex blocks. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple worlds to unlock.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 distinct block-transforming machines.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 100 increasingly complex puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level Editor to create your own levels.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2731590/extras/8864ebf8bcfbe519409c58ec1d0f7862.poster.avif?t=1768428581\" width=614 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2731590/extras/8864ebf8bcfbe519409c58ec1d0f7862.webm?t=1768428581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2731590/extras/8864ebf8bcfbe519409c58ec1d0f7862.mp4?t=1768428581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Block Shop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are one of the final candidates in our search for the new Block Shop Operator. Do you have the problem-solving skills, resourcefulness, and intellect to fill this important role? Only one way to find out... </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Block Shop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Block shop is an automation puzzle game in which basic blocks are transformed and combined to create increasingly complex blocks. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple worlds to unlock.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 distinct block-transforming machines.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 100 increasingly complex puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level Editor to create your own levels.</p></li></ul>",
